  "confidence_tier": "high",
  "industry_note": "Si₃N₄ (Silicon Nitride) — covalent ceramic. 변종: • Sintered (SSN, pressureless): σf 600-800 / E 290 / KIC 6.5 / Tmax 1300°C • HIP'd (Hot Isostatic Press): σf 800-1000 / E 310-320 / KIC 8 / Tmax 1400°C — 가장 high-Q • Reaction-bonded (RBSN): σf 200-300 / E 200 / lower density • Sintered Reaction-Bonded (SRBSN): σf 600-800 ρ 3.17-3."
